column2: Test Case 1:CONDITION:All responses are at the SAME price point
Test Case 2:CONDITION:All responses are at the SAME price point. CONDITION:inbound Simple CUSTOMER order trades all Quantity with PO based on CUSTOMER priority
Test Case 3:CONDITION:All responses are at the SAME price point. CONDITION:inbound Simple CUSTOMER order trades all Quantity with PO based on TIME priority versus second inbound Simple CUSTOMER order

Test Case 4:CONDITION:All responses are at the SAME price point. CONDITION:inbound Simple CUSTOMER order trades all Quantity with PO based on CUSTOMER order priority versus second inbound Simple NON-CUSTOMER [FIRM origin] order. CONDITION:NON-CUSTOMER order comes AFTER CUSTOMER order

Test Case 5:CONDITION:All responses are at the SAME price point. CONDITION:inbound Simple CUSTOMER order trades all Quantity with PO based on CUSTOMER order priority versus second inbound Simple NON-CUSTOMER [BROKER DEALER origin] order. CONDITION:NON-CUSTOMER order comes AFTER CUSTOMER order

Test Case 6:CONDITION:All responses are at the SAME price point. CONDITION:inbound Simple CUSTOMER order trades all Quantity with PO based on CUSTOMER order priority versus second inbound Simple NON-CUSTOMER [MARKET MAKER origin] order. CONDITION:NON-CUSTOMER order comes AFTER CUSTOMER order
Test Case 7:CONDITION:PO and MO have CUSTOMER origins AND both PO and MO are at LMT price. CONDITION:MO crosses the CBOE market on Bid side (price better than CBOE Bid side)
Test Case 8:CONDITION:PO and MO have CUSTOMER origins AND MO LMT. CONDITION:MO crosses the CBOE market on Bid side (price equal to CBOE Bid side)
Test Case 9:CONDITION:PO and MO have MARKET MAKER origins AND both PO and MO are at LMT price. CONDITION:MO crosses the CBOE market on Bid side (price better than CBOE Bid side)
Test Case 10:CONDITION:PO and MO have MARKET MAKER origins AND MO LMT. CONDITION:MO crosses the CBOE market on Bid side (price equal to CBOE Bid side)
Test Case 11:PO LINKS AWAY FULL QUANTITY. CONDITION:PO and MO are CUSTOMERS. CONDITION:RESTING NON-CUSTOMER ORDER
Test Case 12:PO LINKS AWAY FULL QUANTITY. CONDITION:PO CUSTOMER only. CONDITION:RESTING NON-CUSTOMER ORDER
Test Case 13:PO LINKS AWAY FULL QUANTITY. CONDITION:PO and MO are CUSTOMERS. CONDITION:RESTING CUSTOMER ORDER
Test Case 14:PO LINKS AWAY FULL QUANTITY. CONDITION:PO is CUSTOMER only. CONDITION:RESTING CUSTOMER ORDER
Test Case 15:CONDITION:PO and MO have CUSTOMER origins AND PO MKT and MO LMT price
Test Case 16:CONDITION:PO and MO have CUSTOMER origins AND both PO and MO are at LMT price
